OStR Mag. Helmuth Peer is a teacher for maths, information technology and sports 
at Bundesgymnasium und Bundesrealgymnasium Weiz, Austria. Since 2003 he has been 
developing the desktop4education and server4education for the Austrian Federal 
Ministry for Education together with the students Markus Fleck, Matthias 
Praunegger and Stefan Reisinger. This schoolserver (server4education) und client 
(desktop4educaton), which are installed in a lot of Austrian schools already, 
are based on free software.
